// @test regression/INV079-if-condition-leading-binary-wrap
// @description Restricted if-condition parsing must keep valid operator-leading wraps when postfix parsing already consumed the newline before the operator. Multiple-of-4 wraps still fail with TV's newline syntax error. See INV079.
// @expects parse: fail
// @expects error: line=7, column=5, message=/new line/
// @expects ast: body.1.condition.operator = "and"

//@version=6
indicator("INV079")
if close > open
   and high > low
    ok = close
if close > open
    and high > low
    bad = close
plot(close)
